@node Main "Tanglink - Documentation"

                             'Tanglink' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Tanglink' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} based on the average sliding-tiles
puzzle, but with a little twist: in this game, some tiles have
geometric shapes and are linked together. The idea is to move those
tiles at their proper places, so they replicate various patterns...

  Other tiles have no shapes and have no purpose, except than to
complicate the game a little...

  Have fun!

