@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Tanglink" where you want on
your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or Libraries a
are needed. The only requirement is that your Workbench must have at least
4 colours.

                             How to play?

  Playing the game is a simple matter of clicking on any tile that is
located next to the empty space. You can also use the cursor keys from
the keyboard to move the tiles.

  All 'linked' tiles have a geometric figure on them and as you move
those tiles, the links will move accordingly...

  You can click anytime on the '?' tile, located on the lower right of
the game board (or by pressing on the 'Help' key). This will briefly
display the pattern you have to match.

  When completing a game board, the location of the empty space can be
anywhere, except obviously, where a linked shape is supposed to be...

  Try to complete each game board in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

